== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
2008年12月，[[吉勒摩·戴托羅|吉勒摩·戴托羅]]表示有興趣製作一部改編自[[羅爾德·達爾|羅爾德·達爾]]的1983年小說《{{le|女巫 (小說)|The Witches (novel)|女巫}}》的[[定格動畫|定格動畫]]電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://io9.gizmodo.com/5100620/guillermo-del-toro-dances-with-roald-dahls-witches|title=Guillermo Del Toro Dances With Roald Dahl's Witches|first=Meredith|last=Woerner|date=|website=gizmodo.com|accessdate=2018-04-10|archive-date=2016-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508092144/http://io9.gizmodo.com/5100620/guillermo-del-toro-dances-with-roald-dahls-witches|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年6月，[[勞勃·辛密克斯|勞勃·辛密克斯]]被聘來執導電影以及撰寫劇本。戴托羅除了一同撰寫劇本外，還會與辛密克斯和[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]共同製片。辛密克斯描述該片比由{{le|尼可拉斯·羅吉|Nicolas Roeg}}執導的1990年電影《{{le|巫婆 (1990年電影)|The Witches (1990 film)|巫婆}}》更接近原版小說<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/06/robert-zemeckis-the-witches-roald-dahl-1202413871/|title=Robert Zemeckis Taking On Roald Dahl’s ‘The Witches’|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|date=2018-06-20|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809085221/https://deadline.com/2018/06/robert-zemeckis-the-witches-roald-dahl-1202413871/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
2019年1月，宣佈[[安·海瑟薇|安·海瑟薇]]加盟並飾演{{le|高階女巫|Grand High Witch}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/anne-hathaway-the-witches-robert-zemeckis-1203109856/|title=Anne Hathaway to Star in Robert Zemeckis’ ‘The Witches’ (EXCLUSIVE)|first1=Justin|last1=Kroll|date=2019-01-16|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2019-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190128030436/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/anne-hathaway-the-witches-robert-zemeckis-1203109856/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年2月，宣佈[[奧塔薇亞·史班森|奧塔薇亞·史班森]]、新人演員賈薩爾·布魯諾和科迪-雷·伊斯蒂克加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/octavia-spencer-anne-hathaway-witches-adaptation-1203137491/|title=Octavia Spencer Joins Anne Hathaway in ‘Witches’ Adaptation (EXCLUSIVE)|first1=Justin|last1=Kroll|date=2019-02-12|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817080408/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/octavia-spencer-anne-hathaway-witches-adaptation-1203137491/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年5月，[[史丹利·圖奇|史丹利·圖奇]]和[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]加盟劇組<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=https://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/Principal-Photography-Begins-on-Robert-Zemeckis-THE-WITCHES-20190508|title=Principal Photography Begins on Robert Zemeckis' THE WITCHES|first=TV News|last=Desk|website=BroadwayWorld.com|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509042242/https://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwtv/article/Principal-Photography-Begins-on-Robert-Zemeckis-THE-WITCHES-20190508|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月，據透露[[克莉絲汀·錢諾維斯|克莉絲汀·錢諾維斯]]為該片主演之一<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://popculture.com/movies/news/kristin-chenoweth-joins-new-the-witches-adaptation-starring-anne-hathaway/ |title=Kristin Chenoweth Joins New 'The Witches' Adaptation Starring Anne Hathaway |access-date=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107015246/https://popculture.com/movies/news/kristin-chenoweth-joins-new-the-witches-adaptation-starring-anne-hathaway/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2019年5月8日開始進行，拍攝地點包括[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]]的[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]、位於[[哈特福郡|哈特福郡]]的[[華納兄弟利維斯登工作室|華納兄弟利維斯登工作室]]、[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]和[[薩里郡|薩里郡]]的{{le|維吉尼亞沃特湖|Virginia Water Lake}}，拍攝預計於2019年6月25日[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thegww.com/robert-zemeckis-the-witches-adds-octavia-spencer-to-cast/|title=Robert Zemeckis’ ‘The Witches’ Adds Octavia Spencer to Cast|date=2019-02-13|publisher=|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809101307/https://thegww.com/robert-zemeckis-the-witches-adds-octavia-spencer-to-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://hnentertainment.co/wbs-the-witches-remake-starring-anne-hathaway-and-octavia-spencer-expected-to-wrap-filming-on-june-25th/|title=WB’s ‘The Witches’ Remake Starring Anne Hathaway and Octavia Spencer Expected To Wrap Filming On June 25th|first=Christopher|last=Marc|date=2019-03-17|publisher=HNEntertainment.co|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809090817/https://hnentertainment.co/wbs-the-witches-remake-starring-anne-hathaway-and-octavia-spencer-expected-to-wrap-filming-on-june-25th/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年6月19日，一名工作人員在華納兄弟利維斯登工作室被刺傷頸部<ref>{{cite web |last=Mcnary |first=David |url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/the-witches-set-stabbing-anne-hathaway-england-1203248093/ |title=Crew Member Stabbed on Set of Anne Hathaway’s ‘The Witches’ in England |publisher=[[Variety|Variety]] |date=2019-06-19 |accessdate=2012-06-20 |archive-date=2019-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620000528/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/the-witches-set-stabbing-anne-hathaway-england-1203248093/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 音樂 ==
2019年7月19日，宣佈長期與辛密克斯合作的[[亞倫·席維斯崔|亞倫·席維斯崔]]將擔任本片的配樂<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alan Silvestri to Reteam with Robert Zemeckis on ‘The Witches’ {{!}} Film Music Reporter|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/07/17/alan-silvestri-to-reteam-with-robert-zemeckis-on-the-witches/|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816225310/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2019/07/17/alan-silvestri-to-reteam-with-robert-zemeckis-on-the-witches/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《女巫們》在美國於2020年10月22日在[[HBO_Max|HBO Max]]播出，並於2020年10月28日在全球電影院上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/anne-hathaway-robert-zemeckis-movie-roald-dahls-the-witches-heads-to-hbo-max-this-month-1234590081/|title=Anne Hathaway-Robert Zemeckis Movie ‘Roald Dahl’s The Witches’ Heads To HBO Max This Month|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Anthony|last=D’Alessandro|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002205402/https://deadline.com/2020/10/anne-hathaway-robert-zemeckis-movie-roald-dahls-the-witches-heads-to-hbo-max-this-month-1234590081/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前，上映日期曾定於2020年10月9日及2020年10月16日<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/warner-bros-release-dates-galore-doctor-sleep-checks-in-this-november-the-witches-oct-2020-the-suicide-squad-returns-in-2021-1202546092/|title=Warner Bros Release Dates Galore: ‘Doctor Sleep’ Checks In This November, ‘The Witches’ In Fall 2020; ‘The Suicide Squad’ Returns In 2021|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|date=2019-01-31|publisher=|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821003206/https://deadline.com/2019/01/warner-bros-release-dates-galore-doctor-sleep-checks-in-this-november-the-witches-oct-2020-the-suicide-squad-returns-in-2021-1202546092/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/tom-jerry-jumps-to-christmas-2020-the-witches-inches-up-a-week-next-fall-1202769326/|title=‘Tom & Jerry’ Jumps To Christmas 2020, ‘The Witches’ Inches Up A Week Next Fall|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|date=2019-10-25|publisher=|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025193656/https://deadline.com/2019/10/tom-jerry-jumps-to-christmas-2020-the-witches-inches-up-a-week-next-fall-1202769326/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
